<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes rather than fire primarily disturb stands. <i>Baccharis sergiloides </i> and <i>B. emoryi </i>can sprout after disturbance, but we lack information on the alliance's response to fire.</div>
